data.description:
Cute home that has been recently painted both inside and out. Just move in & enjoy! Newer roof, ceiling
insulation, windows, electrical, plumbing, flooring and water heater! This home features a main floor
bedroom. Upstairs has an additional two bedrooms & full bath. The front entry has a lovely screened-in
porch for sitting in and enjoying cool spring/summer/fall breezes. The unfinished basement offers opportunities to increase your living space. The yard is fully fenced. An easy walk or bike ride to
a nearby grocery store, the historic downtown which includes shops, restaurants and schools. Home warranty included.
